#

Creamy Lemon Herb Risotto

$15.99
620 kcal
Difficulty: 50%

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Tags:

ItalianComfort FoodGourmet

Description

A rich and creamy risotto infused with fresh lemon and herbs, perfect for a comforting yet elegant meal.

Ingredients

  • Arborio rice: 1 cup
  • Vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • White wine: 1/2 cup
  • Shallots: 2, finely chopped
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • Lemon juice: 1/4 cup
  • Fresh parsley: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Butter: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
